snippet.title: Astral Ascent - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Astral Ascent is now available on PC, Playstation & Nintendo Switch!

Fight the 12 Almighty Zodiacs with 4 unique heroes and create infinite builds in this colorful lightning fast roguelite!
